  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\n>As a user\r\n>I want to be able to filter notifications by type\r\n>So that I can search for them more effectively\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThis feature is part of a larger effort to create a new Activity Center.\r\n\r\n- [Figma - Activity Center user journeys](https://www.figma.com/file/eDfxTa9IoaCMUy5cLTp0ys/Shell-for-Mobile?node-id=639%3A21926)\r\n- Given that users can accumulate lots of notifications, they should be paginated, and a proper loading indicator should be displayed when necessary. Consider talking to the UX team about this.",
